    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first shot of the Common Sense Destruction Series!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Devil Revesi is an entirely new game that challenges conventional Reversi gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adding new rules to the traditional one, as well as systems and animation unique to digital games, will make you feel like you have a brand-new experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Devilish System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・&quot;Pile&quot; your disk on the grid where another disk is already on!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・&quot;Sacrifice&quot; your disks and summon a &quot;Totem&quot; so your opponent cannot pile on it anymore!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■3Modes awaits you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・You will learn how to play and devise a strategy of Devil Reversi through accomplishing questions from a servant of Devil Kings in Story Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Several difficulty of AI will train you in Single Player Mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Need more thrill? Seek your rivals all over the world! Online Mode allows you to play against players worldwide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Staff</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >＜Character Design＞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >George Kamitani</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hitoshi Sakimoto</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■Cast</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vritra (Voice: Yurina Uchiyama)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Astra (Voice: Mayu Sagara)</p>",
